node.text: Accessories at Mebie Baby! Burp cloths, bibs, socks, head wraps  and hats. ❤️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on August 07, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and baby.

node.text: Happy Saturday! I hope you all enjoy your weekend. We love this organic plum color so much. #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on August 06, 2021.

node.text:
We're kicking off ☀️ August ☀️ the right way... with a G I F T A W A Y ! @mebiebaby and @urbanbabyco are EACH giving a random winner (which could be YOU!) a $100 shop credit. 

TO ENTER:⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
1. Follow @mebiebaby + @urbanbabyco⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
2. Like + save this post
3. Tag your friends + share in your stories!
*BONUS* Comment some of your favorite baby names! 💕💙
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
-Closes 11:59pm MST on 8/8.
-Winner announced on 8/9.
-Open worldwide, shipping and customs charges may apply.⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
-Not affiliated with Instagram.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on August 06, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and baby.

node.text: Sweet baby bundled up! We have so many fun items coming for fall but unfortunately have had multiple shipping delays. So stick with us and understand we will get some good stuff in soon! #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on August 05, 2021.

node.text: New muslin prints in the shop! Arizona Daisy and Sahara. Thanks to everyone who helps us think of names. It’s always fun to see what you all come up with. #mebiebaby

node.text: Three sweet babies in our favorite Organic footies! #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on August 03, 2021.

node.text: This stack just keeps getting bigger + better! Who got the muslin that they wanted yesterday? We are so glad that alpine, wildflower and night sky are back! #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on August 02, 2021.

node.text: There will be muslin restocks today! Stay tuned, watch stories and make sure your signed up for restock notifications if it’s an item you have been wanting! #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on July 31, 2021. May be an image of baby.

node.text: How cute are the vanilla footie and the cream quilt together? 😍 #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on July 30, 2021.

node.text: Such a cute little set! We love the oversized size of the burp cloths. Great for spit up, messes and even changing your baby laying on one! #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on July 29, 2021 tagging @piccalio. May be an image of 1 person, baby and indoor.

node.text: How cute is this? We love that the sizes 6-12 and up in footies now have grips! Your babe can scoot and run around in these without slipping. 👏 #mebiebaby
